ion, we prove\nthe corresponding results and estimates for the system of coupled transport\nequations. The related existence results are given for the adjoint problem as\nwell. We also give some computational points (e.g. certain explicit formulas),\nand we outline a related inverse problem at the end of the paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2016 15:16:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Dec 2016 19:40:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Apr 2018 15:07:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-06"}
